---

The understanding of the Tomb Raider PSX level data formats derives from
the OpenLara project (https://github.com/XProger/OpenLara). This port's
engine code (68000/Tom/Jerry) is original work written for the Jaguar.

Tomb Raider and all its assets are the property of their rights holders.
This repository contains NO game assets. Building requires a disc image of
Tomb Raider (PlayStation, USA v1.6) that you own; assets are extracted
locally on your machine and are never redistributed.
